---
title: BBQ-Rubbed Chicken with Broccoli Salad and Creamy Dill Dressing
description: Unbelievably simple and packed with flavour, this dish brings summer back to your plate. There's nothing like sweet, smoky barbecue flavour on juicy chicken thighs and a creamy, dreamy broccoli salad to pair alongside!
